---
title: Anatomy of a Colab Notebook
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    primaryColor: "#a5d8ff"
    primaryBorderColor: "#4a9eed"
    lineColor: "#555"
  flowchart:
    htmlLabels: true
    curve: basis
---
flowchart TB
    classDef start fill:#a5d8ff,stroke:#4a9eed
    classDef hitl fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#f59e0b,stroke-width:3px
    classDef auto fill:#d0bfff,stroke:#8b5cf6
    classDef done fill:#b2f2bb,stroke:#22c55e

    A["<b>Menu Bar</b><br/>File · Edit · Runtime · Tools"]:::start
    B["<b>Toolbar</b><br/>+ Code &nbsp;&nbsp; + Text &nbsp;&nbsp; shortcuts"]:::start
    C["<b>Runtime Status</b><br/>● Connected / ○ Disconnected"]:::hitl
    D["<b>Code Cell [▶]</b><br/>Type Python here<br/>Execution count [1] [2] …"]:::auto
    E["<b>Output Area</b><br/>Result appears here<br/>after Shift+Enter"]:::done
    F["<b>Text Cell</b><br/>Write explanations<br/>and headings"]:::hitl

    A --> B
    B --> D
    B --> F
    C -.->|"monitors"| D
    D -->|"Shift+Enter"| E
